forkee.name: MCTwilioSMS
forkee.description: Code to process chat messages in Minecraft and send them to a Twilio number

commits.message:
Created tests for receiving

The receiving function continuously cycles to look for incoming text messages, and correctly displays them

Parsed time

Time of message is now shown in local time and as hour:minute

Generalized Sender

Now you can input your own twilio phone number

SmsSender done

SmsSender works and sends messages

Able to obtain texts

Can obtain the bodies of text messages  already received.

Minecraft to text request

Minecraft /me command can be used to give code msg and destination
